title: Star Wars Omnibus - Boba Fett
description:
Published by Dark Horse Comics in 2010. Promotional Blurb - "Collected here are nine stories of Boba Fett's high-risk and high-adventure missions. From settling diplomatic disputies (with extreme prejudice) to a bounty-hunter free-for-all, from a duel with Darth Vader to dealing with Boba Fett imposters, if the price is right, there is no job too perilous for this mysterious man in Mandalorian armor!"

All credit to original scanners. Please seed and enjoy! :-)
